{"id":"cmmekzl450001ao6b63ctb8h1","projectId":"cmmda4tdu00007oqcfk611gwg","campaignId":"cmmekujfn00012ihyp8y1mnei","type":"social_post","subtype":"feed_post","platform":"instagram","title":"Cultural Sensitivity Builds Patient Trust","description":null,"status":"IN_REVIEW","currentVersion":1,"metadata":"{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"post_type\":\"testimonial\",\"target_audience\":\"Healthcare providers\",\"scheduled_time\":\"2026-03-09T18:00:00Z\",\"hashtags\":[\"PatientTrust\",\"CulturalSensitivity\",\"HealthcareExcellence\",\"ZavisHealth\",\"RamadanCare\"],\"day\":3}","tags":null,"createdAt":"2026-03-06T07:36:40.613Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-06T07:46:25.401Z","versions":[{"id":"cmmekzl4o0003ao6b4qqdufvt","assetId":"cmmekzl450001ao6b63ctb8h1","version":1,"filePath":null,"content":"\"When my clinic adjusted their hours for Ramadan and sent me health tips about fasting, I knew they truly cared about me as a person, not just a patient.\"\n\nCultural sensitivity is not a nice-to-have. It is the foundation of patient trust.\n\nThis Ramadan, the small gestures matter most:\n- A simple Ramadan Mubarak greeting\n- Not offering water to fasting patients\n- Adjusting communication timing\n- Sharing relevant health content\n\nTrust is built one interaction at a time.\n\n#PatientTrust #CulturalSensitivity #HealthcareExcellence #ZavisHealth #RamadanCare #PatientExperience #CompassionateCare #HealthTech #InclusiveHealthcare #RamadanMubarak","metadata":"{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"post_type\":\"testimonial\",\"target_audience\":\"Healthcare providers\",\"scheduled_time\":\"2026-03-09T18:00:00Z\",\"hashtags\":[\"PatientTrust\",\"CulturalSensitivity\",\"HealthcareExcellence\",\"ZavisHealth\",\"RamadanCare\"],\"day\":3}","changelog":"Initial generation","createdAt":"2026-03-06T07:36:40.629Z","feedbacks":[]}],"brandChecks":[{"id":"cmmelc4c60001exib2fsupnta","assetId":"cmmekzl450001ao6b63ctb8h1","versionNumber":1,"checkType":"visual_qa","score":90,"passed":true,"details":"{\"text_